00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:12.440
So basically before I joined Pfizer, there was an initiative to streamline the process

00:05:12.440 --> 00:05:19.480
of, you know, bring together the, our users, because when I joined Pfizer, I think it was

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:27.079
about, it was shy to like 1000 people on the Microsoft teams channel and Pfizer who were

