And I really want to acknowledge your help with it because what happened is we reached

00:11:35.559 --> 00:11:41.479
out to you asking if you could share your expertise, your knowledge, your experience,

00:11:41.479 --> 00:11:48.119
because coming to the hangout and it's totally different piece from facilitating it.

00:11:48.119 --> 00:11:53.080
And I know it's probably so much going on in the background to actually putting this

00:11:53.080 --> 00:11:54.359
whole thing together.

00:11:54.359 --> 00:11:58.760
So you're very responsive when I actually reached out and we set up the meeting and

00:11:58.760 --> 00:12:00.039
ask a few questions.

00:12:02.280 --> 00:12:09.479
Having the hangout, I think, within the organization is very valuable because of the added

00:12:09.479 --> 00:12:14.679
aspect of actually talking about certain things within the organization.

00:12:14.679 --> 00:12:21.000
So, for example, if I come to this hangout and we discuss certain questions, I get certain

00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:22.440
questions, we discuss certain topics.

00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:27.239
Sometimes I might say, well, this is a great question, but I can't talk about it because

00:12:27.239 --> 00:12:32.919
the information is proprietary, like I can't really share it, which if you do the hangout

00:12:32.919 --> 00:12:35.719
within your organization, you don't have to worry about that.

00:12:36.679 --> 00:12:41.559
All people work kind of on the same project or on different projects, but you can share

00:12:41.559 --> 00:12:43.559
the information together.

00:12:43.559 --> 00:12:50.280
And this is how certain problems get solved faster or issues people are running into.

00:12:50.280 --> 00:12:56.280
And then it also brings people together that wouldn't work together necessarily.

00:12:57.479 --> 00:13:01.880
And I think this is a very valuable part of it.

00:13:02.760 --> 00:13:08.200
Such a great point to bring people together that wouldn't have naturally been working

00:13:08.200 --> 00:13:09.239
on projects.

