00:32:13.180 --> 00:32:16.380
using SAS for many, many years.

00:32:16.380 --> 00:32:19.739
And they built great technical expertise.

00:32:19.739 --> 00:32:22.380
And they mostly work in SAS.

00:32:22.380 --> 00:32:32.699
And maybe they need to know why we need to start using R in certain projects.

00:32:32.699 --> 00:32:36.540
