00:32:36.540 --> 00:32:39.660
Or they want to be in their SAS world.

00:32:40.939 --> 00:32:49.420
But I think it's important for us to communicate and create this community of users why R is

00:32:49.420 --> 00:32:52.780
important and where the industry is moving.

00:32:52.780 --> 00:33:00.859
But we don't tell people to stop using SAS and start using R.

00:33:00.859 --> 00:33:02.619
