00:36:58.540 --> 00:37:02.699
One of the biggest hurdles I've had is people thinking that, oh, I have to have this perfect

00:37:02.699 --> 00:37:03.659
to talk about it.

00:37:03.659 --> 00:37:04.860
No, no, no, no.

00:37:04.860 --> 00:37:11.500
Sometimes my biggest mishaps end up leading to an innovative solution, but you don't get

00:37:11.500 --> 00:37:16.300
the full story just by looking at the end product, getting the process there, and being,

00:37:16.300 --> 00:37:21.419
I hate to say vulnerable, but being comfortable with sharing those stumbling blocks.

00:37:21.419 --> 00:37:25.659
I'm comfortable with it, but definitely want to help others feel comfortable with that

00:37:25.659 --> 00:37:25.820
